性。<br />\n<br />\n你亦都可以理解後現代為對現代主義嘅回應/批判。現代主義大概就係發展至上、物質至上，資本主義啱啱全速前進之際。後現代就會批判呢種物質至上嘅諗法。但後現代亦都可以用黎形容資本主義進一步變得猖狂，猖狂到人類冇辦法唔跟隨資本主義嘅一種社會狀態。<br />\n<br />\n回應你問題，未來比較似係一個概念，而後現代比較似係一個時代嘅形容詞/概括詞。希望唔會講得太一舊舊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0034d3f22a9f0160d9b83efcc03afe34edb8a776","tid":2076493,"uid":128896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca6360e4a782c8d35b8c71dec69e01fa8d97f81d","tid":2076493,"uid":201031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc6e26372c83b566793466ed1dcbcb794bb7a06","tid":2076493,"uid":128896,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"681b1a7ca406609565146a6bf74acc97c6b15e61","tid":2076493,"uid":125498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:15:58.000Z","msg":"點解要叫後現代？<br />\n點解唔叫未來？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"因為後現代唔代表係未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣義而言 佢更似係一個用思想區分嘅時期"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T18:00:24.000Z","msg":"後現代之後仲可以叫咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T12:02:05.000Z","msg":"有人係propose post-postmodernism<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aba9115cde2c5dc0735b73b96f44670111eea957","tid":2076493,"uid":360830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4cefae13aec526d6b0609851dc96b94601e777c7","tid":2076493,"uid":128896,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"535ec1c1fdd89962e260fca045815715dab320d6","tid":2076493,"uid":12421,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5dc6e26372c83b566793466ed1dcbcb794bb7a06","tid":2076493,"uid":128896,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-23T14:21:03.000Z","msg":"因為後現代唔代表係未來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n廣義而言 佢更似係一個用思想區分嘅時期"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T11:45:33.000Z","msg":"咁未來代表